    "keep": "保留",
    "targetPage": "students.html",
    "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<h1 class=\"size-64 is-title1-64 is-title-bold\">2023全國高中科學班免試保送三名<br />\n獵豹學子獨佔兩名</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">許庭誠同學 建中科學班<br />\n(參與課程:<span style=\"background-color:#dddddd;\">GM國中資優, FS高中輕競賽, FA高階賽</span>)<br />\n<br />\n林峻丞同學 雄中科學班<br />\n(參與課程:<span style=\"background-color:#dddddd;\"> FS高中輕競賽, FA高階賽, FUC微積分</span>)<br />\n---<br />\n詳情請見下方臉書連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1250440772575272/\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1250440772575272/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "bodyText": "2023全國高中科學班免試保送三名 獵豹學子獨佔兩名 許庭誠同學 建中科學班 (參與課程: GM國中資優, FS高中輕競賽, FA高階賽 ) 林峻丞同學 雄中科學班 (參與課程: FS高中輕競賽, FA高階賽, FUC微積分 ) --- 詳情請見下方臉書連結: https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1250440772575272/",
